#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
#. VAR: ca rūpasaññaṃ → ye ca rūpasaññā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an9.33:5.1"
msgid "Yattha rūpasaññā nirujjhati, ye ca rūpasaññaṃ nirodhetvā nirodhetvā viharanti, ‘addhā te āyasmanto nicchātā nibbutā tiṇṇā pāraṅgatā tadaṅgenā’ti vadāmi. "
msgstr "Where perceptions of form ceases, and those who have thoroughly ended perceptions of form meditate, I say: ‘Clearly those venerables are desireless, extinguished, crossed over, and gone beyond in that respect.’ "

msgctxt "an9.33:5.2"
msgid "‘Kattha rūpasaññā nirujjhati, ke ca rūpasaññaṃ nirodhetvā nirodhetvā viharanti—"
msgstr "If someone should say, ‘I do not know or see where perceptions of form ceases’, "

msgctxt "an9.33:5.3"
msgid "ahametaṃ na jānāmi ahametaṃ na passāmī’ti, iti yo evaṃ vadeyya, so evamassa vacanīyo: "
msgstr "they should be told: "

msgctxt "an9.33:5.4"
