msgstr "Where the perception of the dimension of infinite space ceases, and those who have thoroughly ended the perception of the dimension of infinite space meditate, I say: ‘Clearly those venerables are desireless, extinguished, crossed over, and gone beyond in that respect.’ "

msgctxt "an9.33:6.2"
msgid "‘Kattha ākāsānañcāyatanasaññā nirujjhati, ke ca ākāsānañcāyatanasaññaṃ nirodhetvā nirodhetvā viharanti—"
msgstr "If someone should say, ‘I do not know or see where the perception of the dimension of infinite space ceases’, "

msgctxt "an9.33:6.3"
msgid "ahametaṃ na jānāmi ahametaṃ na passāmī’ti, iti yo evaṃ vadeyya, so evamassa vacanīyo: "
msgstr "they should be told: "

